statements.sql: select `matselements`.`Name`, `matdetails`.`Qty`, sum(orderdetails.Qty) as Qtyo from `matdetails` inner join `mats` on `mats`.`Guid` = `matdetails`.`MatGuid` inner join `matselements` on `matselements`.`Guid` = `matdetails`.`MatElementGuid` inner join `orderdetails` on `orderdetails`.`MatGuid` = `matdetails`.`MatGuid` inner join `orders` on `orders`.`Guid` = `orderdetails`.`OrderGuid` where `orders`.`Date` between '2021-01-19 00:00:00' and '2021-01-19 23:59:59' group by `matselements`.`Name`, `matdetails`.`Qty`
